{"tid":57172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖情人、控制狂，你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-27T19:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T20:55:08.000Z","uid":29846,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67700a06cb94db8d57e963c661d7e1aaa701340d","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:43:58.000Z","msg":"絲打 拍過四次拖 任任都好聽話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趁而家人少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩想知即管問啦"},{"pid":"11fa824b3482e3b19a73f006c92ed5a622c027cc","tid":57172,"uid":7360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:48:12.000Z","msg":"反抗有咩後果"},{"pid":"fc05c53aecacbd40494af97e229e084bbb67e263","tid":57172,"uid":67443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:50:46.000Z","msg":"點做到？有咩技巧？<br />\n聽話仲乜飛？"},{"pid":"27d71cf6d6c4a0f9109a766bbed7cf3fd22b2483","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反抗有咩後果</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要睇吓係啲乜，不過未有人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf9ecc68b104893718873c9a5a37419747b67e2","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點做到？有咩技巧？<br />\n聽話仲乜飛？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔知，一直諗緊係我好彩定我真係有乜魔力令到佢哋咁死心塌地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n任任都唔同，曾經有一任我對佢實在太仆街，頂唔順走咗，自此之後我就收斂咗少少"},{"pid":"cd637f5ca8998f8866440b449d7d677e5f77af02","tid":57172,"uid":67612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:56:19.000Z","msg":"用咩方法留住佢地又甘願繼續比你咁做"},{"pid":"075ab3d4b255dcf973980243650ac4ac5d3721cf","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用咩方法留住佢地又甘願繼續比你咁做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能因為我拍拖同其他人唔同，我比較似男仔，佢哋發生咩事我會用理性開解佢哋、照顧佢哋嘅感受、當佢哋好似女仔咁錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢哋覺得我同其他女仔唔一樣。<br />\n但當然啦，我係好錫佢哋，但相反代價係要畀我知道、控制哂一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28668dc09d03cfb3aaa29a5fcfbf2f73010160d","tid":57172,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:16:05.000Z","msg":"我可唔可以同你一齊，好似好有安全感"},{"pid":"b6c24cb17872717de043c0c52503f827c46d4bc1","tid":57172,"uid":23836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:16:07.000Z","msg":"最恐佈係乜事"},{"pid":"91af2c8ce74f22e7e6bb84ce3e2c881b6e75f6f8","tid":57172,"uid":67612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用咩方法留住佢地又甘願繼續比你咁做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能因為我拍拖同其他人唔同，我比較似男仔，佢哋發生咩事我會用理性開解佢哋、照顧佢哋嘅感受、當佢哋好似女仔咁錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢哋覺得我同其他女仔唔一樣。<br />\n但當然啦，我係好錫佢哋，但相反代價係要畀我知道、控制哂一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁之後又係因咩原因離開你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c6aeaec506f02772d7a50cf93bf5250f158e9d","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我可唔可以同你一齊，好似好有安全感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有男朋友了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae0b4e6e1be15fa6a4bbce00e05619e7abf32d5","tid":57172,"uid":23282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:20:33.000Z","msg":"做愛正常唔正常？會唔會控制埋個節奏"},{"pid":"226f6c9430d7e56668912be2755414135bb541f3","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最恐佈係乜事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最恐怖就廢時喺到講喇，而家最多都係燒哂啲嘢、打吓交、掉爛佢部電話（最後件事解決咗我就會幫佢整返/買部新嘅畀佢）"},{"pid":"43b0f9d61db273f0cc60761100154e9260254d46","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用咩方法留住佢地又甘願繼續比你咁做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能因為我拍拖同其他人唔同，我比較似男仔，佢哋發生咩事我會用理性開解佢哋、照顧佢哋嘅感受、當佢哋好似女仔咁錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢哋覺得我同其他女仔唔一樣。<br />\n但當然啦，我係好錫佢哋，但相反代價係要畀我知道、控制哂一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁之後又係因咩原因離開你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除咗第三任，冇人離開過我，係我離開佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於點解同第三任散，上面有講"},{"pid":"f20382cdc5f98ff93b2ec6a32bc54d49747ca411","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做愛正常唔正常？會唔會控制埋個節奏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做愛反而係相反，喺床上我鍾意畀人控制、SM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369826897b892f68dbe8240336cd2ff4205d6c0f","tid":57172,"uid":41201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:33:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母自私撚，抵你比人中咁多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1cbd8abd1a470b90c422c46b8f21c268a59c70","tid":57172,"uid":68301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:35:55.000Z","msg":"我fd有個ex試過係街到叫我fd蚊住耳仔行   掉爆個玻璃瓶汁起塊玻璃夾係手指到一巴車洛去，，跟住拎把介刀追住我fd我fd鎖住自己係厠所佢係出面插對面，，見佢洛左冷靜d出番黎望到個電腦mon介花曬，，，同埋屈斷兩部電話  自己揸住條仔部機放相話好愛個女仔"},{"pid":"a2b07f1a6f7bfe99e4db27677024c7c6de09f9a2","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母自私撚，抵你比人中咁多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思漏咗講，我諗好多人以為我係平時對佢哋好仆街、畀帽佢戴、呃鳩佢錢乜乜柒柒，呢啲叫港女。<br />\n至於我係比一般人拍拖擺放更多愛落去，順境逆境我會陪你一齊捱、冇錢出街食飯我畀錢你、想要啲乜嘢就送畀你、畀安全感你，但前提係你要比我愛你更加愛我、聽教聽話、你嘅世界只可以有我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1d95b208217dd5aef8683001184cacee5abe45","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我fd有個ex試過係街到叫我fd蚊住耳仔行   掉爆個玻璃瓶汁起塊玻璃夾係手指到一巴車洛去，，跟住拎把介刀追住我fd我fd鎖住自己係厠所佢係出面插對面，，見佢洛左冷靜d出番黎望到個電腦mon介花曬，，，同埋屈斷兩部電話  自己揸住條仔部機放相話好愛個女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又過份咗少少，會嚴重傷害他人身體嗰啲我唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2112fca830ffee18cd7795226c8581b522509126","tid":57172,"uid":67612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能因為我拍拖同其他人唔同，我比較似男仔，佢哋發生咩事我會用理性開解佢哋、照顧佢哋嘅感受、當佢哋好似女仔咁錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢哋覺得我同其他女仔唔一樣。<br />\n但當然啦，我係好錫佢哋，但相反代價係要畀我知道、控制哂一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁之後又係因咩原因離開你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除咗第三任，冇人離開過我，係我離開佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於點解同第三任散，上面有講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因咩離開佢地？有無求番你復合？"},{"pid":"f8b55de0e2a394398429df6f5b1a2e3e13be8bf8","tid":57172,"uid":5684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:51:46.000Z","msg":"好撚想俾人控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不肻好似樓主咁又好似太over<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0fe310ae1ccdefab5843ffafe3d163295eb5c6","tid":57172,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁之後又係因咩原因離開你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除咗第三任，冇人離開過我，係我離開佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於點解同第三任散，上面有講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因咩離開佢地？有無求番你復合？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想佢搵返啲正常女仔拍拖。<br />\n有求返我復合，但始終我呢種人唔啱佢，散都係遲早嘅事。"}]}